Transportation Minister Rotimi Amaechi, has said that his wife, Judith, got to understand why he spends so much time on the Lagos-Ibadan rail project after she accompanied him on an inspection tour. The minister, who tweeted this via his Twitter handle @ChibuikeAmaechi, did not state when the inspection tour took place. Amaechi praised his wife, saying, “Her support is unquantifiable.” See the tweet: 